nodes.text: Qlint was a terrestrial astronomical object in the galaxy. At some point by 3 ABY, the assassin Just Lucky attempted to kill the rogue archaeologist Doctor Chelli Aphra on Qlint. Sometime later, while working alongside Aphra, Lucky saved her from the bounty hunter Tubleek Ruz, and Aphra claimed that the two were even for his previous attempt to kill her.
Qlint was first mentioned in the comic Doctor Aphra 1, written by Alyssa Wong and published digitally by Marvel Comics on May 4, 2020.
